### Create Goal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Improve Code Quality",
  "description": "Increase test coverage to 80%",
  "weightage": 30.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 1
}

