### Get Goal by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Goal not found (404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Goals by User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Goal
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/goals/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Improve Code Quality Updated",
  "description": "Increase test coverage to 90%",
  "weightage": 30.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 1
}

